OL,3,CPonies found in 'shocking' state at
OL,4,Chorse therapy centre
OL,6,FThree people have been sentenced after
OL,7,Fponies were found in a 'shocking'
OL,8,Fstate at an horse therapy centre in
OL,9,FCornwall.
OL,11,FThe ponies were left without enough
OL,12,Ffood, water or shelter in 27 degree
OL,13,Fheat, with rescuers saying it was the
OL,14,Fworst case they had ever worked on.
OL,16,FThe Mare and Foal Sanctuary, in
OL,17,FNewton Abbot, were contacted by a
OL,18,Fconcerned member of the public in 2021
OL,19,Fand have been nursing the animals back
OL,20,Fto health.
