OL,6,FSenior welfare advisor Rebecca
OL,7,FSherrell was involved in the rescue.
OL,8,FShe said: "It was the worst case I've
OL,9,Fever worked on.
OL,11,F"I've never seen horses that thin
OL,12,Fbefore. They were lacking food, water
OL,13,Fand shelter in 27 degree heat. It's a
OL,14,Fcase that has really stuck with me.
OL,16,F"Many of the equines were in a very
OL,17,Fpoor state with conjunctivitis, lice,
OL,18,Fmalnourishment, worm burden, overgrown
OL,19,Fhooves, heart conditions, alopecia,
OL,20,Fanemia and chronic inflammation.
