OL,6,F"Their bones showed through their
OL,7,Fskin, and some were covered in paint
OL,8,Fbrush marks from children's parties.
OL,9,FWe also believe some were showing
OL,10,Fsigns of severe depression. It was
OL,11,Fshocking to see, especially at a place
OL,12,Fwhich claimed to offer equine assisted
OL,13,Ftherapy."
OL,15,FSarah Baker, Darren Laker and James
OL,16,FBaker were sentenced at Truro Crown
OL,17,FCourt for animal welfare offences
OL,18,Frelating to animals they kept and
OL,19,Fcared for at Family Nest Therapy in
OL,20,FPar, Cornwall.
