OL,3,CPonies found in 'shocking' state at
OL,4,Chorse therapy centre
OL,6,FSarah Jayne Baker and James Baker both
OL,7,Fof Eastcliffe Road in Par, were
OL,8,Fsentenced to nine months in prison,
OL,9,Fsuspended for two years, and
OL,10,Fdisqualified from owning animals for
OL,11,Flife.
OL,13,FDarren Paul Laker, of Snowland Caravan
OL,14,FSite in Par was sentenced to 12 weeks
OL,15,Fin prison, suspended for two years,
OL,16,Fand disqualified from owning horses
OL,17,Ffor 10 years, with no right to appeal
OL,18,Ffor five years.
