OL,6,FAfter more than a year recovering with
OL,7,Fthe charity, having fully regained
OL,8,Ftheir health, three Shetlands; Poppy,
OL,9,FSherbert and Lola now have lifelong
OL,10,Fsanctuary with The Mare and Foal
OL,11,FSanctuary and are thriving.
OL,13,FThe Mare and Foal Sanctuary provided
OL,14,F14 months of rehabilitation to the
OL,15,Fponies. They're now providing
OL,16,Fpermanent lifelong care to three of
OL,17,Fthe Shetland ponies involved.
